&quot;In general, our advice is to develop a responsive site that can adapt to the capabilities of different devices. If you choose to build a mobile-specific experience then we recommend looking for the sub-string &quot;mobile&quot; in the user agent string to determine when to deliver mobile optimised content:&quot;<p><pre><code>    function isMobile() {
        return navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf(&quot;mobile&quot;)>=0;
    }
</code></pre>
This is really the best we can do after twenty years of the WWW?
